&lt;p&gt;This looks like a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6716&quot; title=&quot;osc_io_submit()) ASSERTION( osc == oap-&amp;gt;oap_obj ) failed: &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6716&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6716&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but that was marked as a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3259&quot; title=&quot;cl_lock refactoring&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3259&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3259&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  That ticket had two patches land to master, but only one landed to b2_7_fe.  Assuming that&apos;s actually the fix for this issue, can we get patch 10859 backported to b2_7_fe?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
